    LTEXT           "Thank you for using the HOOPS 3D Stream Control from Tech Soft 3D.",IDC_STATIC,11,71,252,12
    LTEXT           "This control enables you to stream 2D and 3D information over the web.  You can web-publish your own models by exporting HSF from your application.",IDC_STATIC,11,85,252,27
    LTEXT           "This control and the HOOPS Stream File (HSF) toolkit are both components of the HOOPS 3D Application Framework which is used by a wide array of developers to build some of the world's leading CAD/CAM/CAE applications.",IDC_STATIC,11,108,252,32
    LTEXT           "For more information on licensing the framework please contact us directly at \n+1 510 883 2180 or info@techsoft3d.com",IDC_STATIC,11,139,253,18
